---
title: Creamy Rosemary King Prawn Spaghetti with Charred Courgette
description: This Creamy Rosemary King Prawn Spaghetti is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
